{"tid":2341040,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"工作細胞結局篇打武肺","createTime":"2020-12-26T04:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T17:01:31.000Z","uid":187412,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc04c5af3b9484d9e071913d0a09fe1a3b740635","tid":2341040,"uid":187412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"《工作細胞》漫畫進入最終篇：決戰肺炎「新型コロナウイルス」(新型冠狀病毒)<br />\n<br />\n相信有不少讀者都有幻想過，《工作細胞》會談及肺炎，然後它真的跟上時事了，而且更是完結篇的最後高潮世紀決戰！在12月26日推出的《月刊少年天狼星》 (月刊少年シリウス)中，將會有《工作細胞》29話的連載 (新型冠狀病毒 上篇)，而在1月26日就會有30話 (新型冠狀病毒 下篇)。就看看最後人類怎樣擊敗它吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366285370148044/posts/3369747619801789/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366285370148044%2Fposts%2F3369747619801789%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=d3cc8e60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366285370148044/posts/3369747619801789/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdd63f0c1ad2fdda169b1b3d8c8b5b42eb3f53e","tid":2341040,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"想睇dark版女版白血球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67f7599ff9699a03b8688b7941e6055a030cd8b","tid":2341040,"uid":48026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1283182123483095045/GiVsVYY1_400x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F1283182123483095045%2FGiVsVYY1_400x400.jpg&h=2762de70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e11363304e47a9d3ccf92be5e7fa6fc4a7ae6bfa","tid":2341040,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"辱華？"